# Atlas — Environment Variables (Day 1 STUB)
# Day 1: none of these are required. The app runs without any .env file.
# Day 2+: copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values.

# === Day 2: Clerk (Authentication) ===
# Get these from https://dashboard.clerk.com/apps/app_3FEQTBmLTJIH5mTcoRGzJgKnfbt
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
# CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...

# === Day 2: Supabase (Postgres) ===
# Create a project at https://supabase.com/dashboard, then:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxx.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...

# === Day 3: MiniMax (AI) ===
# Alex's MiniMax API access — wired on Day 3.
# MINIMAX_API_KEY=...

# === Day 4: Mapbox (Maps) ===
# Get from https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.eyJ1...

# === Week 2: Connector API keys ===
# Property24, Private Property, Google Places, CoinGecko, GitHub, Reddit, etc.
# Wired one at a time in Week 2.
